A Nigerian sports Journalist, Ibitoye has recently shared the video of a lady he met in Ilorin who said she is ready to donate her kidney to the ailing daughter of the Former deputy senate President of Nigeria, Ike Ekweremadu.
In the video shared by the sports Journalist, the lady, who gave her name as Marta said that she has been told in her dreams to donate her kidney to the daughter of the politician. Marta went on to say that the ailing daughter of the politician is dying, and she wants to help her.
While being asked what her demands are for wanting to help the politician, Marta said that she does not have any demand for now, all she would like to do is to help the ailing girl because time is running out. Marta said she has been having the dream where she has been told to donate her kidney to the ailing daughter of the politician.
You can watch the video of Marta expressing her willingness to donate her kidney here.
It would be recalled that the former deputy senate President, Ike Ekweremadu and his wife, Beatrice Nwanneka Ekweremadu were both arrested in the United Kingdom for an alleged organ harvesting related offence.


